cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper focuses on visual recognition, specifically face recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the interpretability of deep CNNs, which is a topic of interest in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper proposes a method to improve the robustness of face recognition to occlusions, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and computer security (cs.CR).
